{"tid":934703,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"入境處：持有人任何時候只會持有一本有效特區護照","createTime":"2018-12-09T13:05:08.000Z","updateTime":"2018-12-10T16:20:32.000Z","uid":173631,"like":274,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":90,"replies":[{"pid":"81cbf196b480b6e07ac47be99db07667015287c9","tid":934703,"uid":173631,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-09T13:05:08.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"http://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1432451-20181209.htm\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1432451-20181209.htm&d=zI4jTfJbMFlomC76MbivgDCdMQr7etzq9tFbjrA%2B72k%3D&h=4e273de7\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=http%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1432451-20181209.htm&h=ae4e8c00\" target=\"_blank\">http://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1432451-20181209.htm</a><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">孟晚周如何解釋？？</span></span><br />\n<br />\n華為集團副董事長孟晚舟在加拿大被捕，美國司法部指她過去十一年，曾擁有四本中國護照及三本特區護照。入境處回應傳媒查詢時指，特區護照持有人任何時候，只會持有一本有效特區護照。<br />\n<br />\n入境處表示，按現行做法，特區護照持有人可在護照有效期屆滿時，申請換領新的特區護照，但在一些特殊情況下，如護照遺失、損毀或申請人個人資料有所變更，持有人可申請提前換領特區護照。<br />\n<br />\n入境處在簽發新護照時，申請人必須將其所持有的舊護照交回處方註銷，入境處以剪角方式註銷護照後，會將該護照交還給申請人，如有特殊需要，例如申請人的舊護照內，仍貼有其他國家的有效簽證，申請人可以在申請換領特區護照時，同時向入境處申請將舊護照和新的護照拼合，而拼合護照是在舊護照和新護照上作出一項批註，說明舊護照內載有一個仍然有效的簽證，但舊護照因已剪角所以已確定無效。"},{"pid":"b407b8a41506c702ac23d656250c4aafeb591a67","tid":934703,"uid":7555,"like":292,"dislike":3,"score":289,"citedBy":4,"replyTime":"2018-12-09T13:08:58.000Z","msg":"啫係假護照啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/photo.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5a0a77845a9f740fe36acd0ad0bca76d6a873d20","tid":934703,"uid":108467,"like":2,"dislike":3,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-09T13:11:10.000Z","msg":"個別事件？"},{"pid":"50d5656edec8d0fe31aeb80ca739aa28340c8d4d","tid":934703,"uid":113626,"like":269,"dislike":1,"score":268,"quote":{"pid":"b407b8a41506c702ac23d656250c4aafeb591a67","tid":934703,"uid":7555,"like":292,"dislike":3,"score":289,"citedBy":4,"replyTime":"2018-12-09T13:08:58.000Z","msg":"啫係假護照啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/photo.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-09T13:11:46.000Z","msg":"傻啦, 呢d叫出事果事極速割席. <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/no.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8025f4e1ff6818d89827fc246274b2c714cfc0b4","tid":934703,"uid":98431,"like":143,"dislike":0,"score":143,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-09T13:11:49.000Z","msg":"又玩語言偽術<br />\n<br />\n難為班YAHOO爪牙咁夜仲要開工"},{"pid":"d5aa36159f576d22c8fb89e272b78260c96458fa","tid":934703,"uid":76310,"like":12,"dislike":1,"score":11,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-09T13:12:40.000Z","msg":"中間果本有效出入加拿大, 最新果本梗係有效啦<br />\n繼續撐啦"},{"pid":"a568c153458b115560e80452b39e483d3926b7c9","tid":934703,"uid":54264,"like":163,"dislike":1,"score":162,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-09T13:13:22.000Z","msg":"華為「太子女」、副董事長孟晚舟現時仍在加拿大被扣押。加國法院引述美國司法部資料，指孟在過去11年至少有7本護照，當中包括3本香港特區護照，令人關注孟會否同時持多本有效的香港護照<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">。據美國司法部提供的孟晚舟特區護照號碼號作粗簡略推算，孟晚舟最近2次更換護照，分別只相隔約96日和37日</span></span>。立法會議員楊岳橋促請政府盡快交代，以免事件影響香港聲譽。對於孟同時持有中國護照及香港護照，楊亦質疑她在申請香港護照時，作出虛假聲明。<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.news.appledaily.com/local/realtime/article/20181209/59010683\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20181209%2F59010683&d=zI4jTfJbMFlomC76MbivgDCdMQr7etzq9tFbjrA%2B72k%3D&h=eae3212f\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20181209%2F59010683&h=85a94c01\" target=\"_blank\">https://hk.news.appledaily.com/local/realtime/article/20181209/59010683</a>"},{"pid":"3f1e5ef510782ed7e166a49a1309ec12d873070b","tid":934703,"uid":13257,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-09T13:13:47.000Z","msg":"第二本<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"